        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/3/1",
        "text": [
          " سَمِعْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ يَقُولُ: «تَارِكُ اَلزَّكَاةِ وَ قَدْ وَجَبَتْ لَهُ مِثْلُ مَانِعِهَا وَ قَدْ وَجَبَتْ عَلَيْهِ»."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.1596 - Marwan ibn Muslim reported from Abdullah ibn Hilal, who said:\nI heard Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) say:\n\"The one who neglects Zakat after it has become obligatory upon him is like the one who withholds it after it has become due.\""
          ]
        }
